Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========TEXT============
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.44,0:00:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶像  如月千早所隐藏的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.87,0:00:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.81,0:00:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了跑到千早姐姐身边的弟弟遭遇车祸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.41,0:00:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开了人世
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.25,0:00:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时千早8岁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据当场围观人群的证言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早完全没有去救弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.22,0:00:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一味地旁观
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她对弟弟见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.14,0:00:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片上是在弟弟墓前争吵的千早和她们的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺带一提千早的父母在数个月前就离婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外死亡  家庭瓦解  离婚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的身边充满的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:00:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如月千早就这样掩藏着咒怨的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:00:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也依然在无知的粉丝们面前歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.13,0:01:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好像一切都是千早的错一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.47,0:01:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是充满恶意的文章
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早居然还有弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.82,0:01:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  你听说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.46,0:01:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经有过弟弟  他也是因为我才丧生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟的事我从你父母那里也有听说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是碰巧在现场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有什么责任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和父母说什么没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…要是没有我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.94,0:01:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟就不会遇上车祸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如月君…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.16,0:01:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须继续唱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.31,0:01:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只是为了弟弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,765事务所  你肯定没想到我还有这么一招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.49,0:02:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是已经能想像高木那沮丧的脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的做法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.02,0:02:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说别耍这种小聪明了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用尽卑鄙手段的不是大叔你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在和谁说话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.81,0:02:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该说过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们给我闭上嘴服从命令就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就看着三流事务所自取灭亡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗓子应该没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发声也应该没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想唱却发不出声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样恐怕是精神上的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也有随着时间慢慢恢复的例子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我也不好说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱吧  唱吧  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时弟弟是我唯一的观众
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到那一刻…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须继续唱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了优  我必须继续唱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么想的…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不能为他唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为偶像  作为姐姐  都失职了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早  别太放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌的工作暂且休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先好好调整心态…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然唱不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不打算继续这份工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定还能唱出来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  一定能的  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你们添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直播吗！？  SUNDAY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天千早因为感冒请假
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以由我们两个为大家主持
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YEAH  加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么首先是这个栏目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,V  在播片了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早还是不接电话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算去她家也不开门
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过为了保证她的正常进餐  倒是下了不少功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母那边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算跟他们说明情况  他们还是「我们也没办法」的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候真希望他们能支持下千早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去下个月的常规演唱会也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs20}如月千早  被揭开的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs20}接二连三的麻烦  已经有了隐退的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}765事务所又现问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs20}如月千早在墓前的争吵\N家庭瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs20}偶像如月千早所隐藏的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早  在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是春香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:05:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  想问你一起去参加舞蹈的课程吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  活动下身子心情也会舒畅些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  大家托我带来了些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶呀  喉糖呀  有好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说拿不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家却还一件件塞给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都快变成圣诞老人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不能再唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经回应不了大家的心意了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早说过是为了弟弟才唱的是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再单纯点不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为喜欢唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为自己想要唱才唱  不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今已经不能这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早对自己太过苛刻了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「因为自己想唱才唱」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样想的话会心情会更轻松一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样如果能再一起唱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天国的弟弟也一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香怎么能…明白我和优
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再多管闲事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:07:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是天海春香吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是如月千早的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话来事务所…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  请把这个交给千早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去世的儿子的画册
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早弟弟的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.24,0:08:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儿子真的很喜欢千早的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是喊着「唱吧  唱吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是让她回想起过去的美好时光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早多少也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  比起我去转交
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是由伯母交给她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算去见她  也只会吵架而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我去安慰她也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  比起我还是伯母比较…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今  已经不存在任何信赖了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们母女一直都是这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再多管闲事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做的  只有这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是交出了这个就回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然千早还是由我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来没精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我是不是很多管闲事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  突然这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早这么说我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.91,0:10:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说「别再多管闲事了」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是会说「加油吧  加油吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.09,0:10:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是千早  对大家都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说这么做只是多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是给大家添麻烦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是那么乐观  这不就是春香的优点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要鼓励别人  还客气那怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.34,0:11:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的那颗牛奶糖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.14,0:11:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我想重新当回大家的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很感谢春香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作人先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  我觉得虽然千早不善言辞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是能理解别人的心意的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香的心意一定传达到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照自己想的把感受全部传达出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是千早拿着麦克风微笑着的画
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是春香的画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  美希
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是千早弟弟的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  那么这就是千早了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没见过像这样唱着歌的千早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希也觉得是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要唱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了优  我必须继续唱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我希望尽可能给千早留下出场空间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要是在歌迷面前失败的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就真的会失去信心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  但是趁这种意识还没扎根  这是个很好的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说  常规演唱会的话风险也不是很大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:12:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  有件事想和你商量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如月千早现在仍然处于活动停止状态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实啊  已经这么久了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.13,0:13:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊  今天有东西想交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能打开门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:14:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不想要  不要再管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能不管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我还想和千早一起工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起站在舞台上  一起歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道这是多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  就算这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是希望千早能继续做偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这个  我放到邮箱里面了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给千早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:15:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很突然  但是给你写了一首新歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是765事务的大家一起作的词
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后让作曲家谱的曲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想着「要如何把现在我们大家的心情传递给你」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「对了  就用歌曲吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很高兴地赞成了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是第一次作词  可能作得不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我们每一个人对千早的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部倾注到这首歌里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起歌唱这大家一起创作的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后让千早露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  就像你弟弟画里的那个女孩子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有呢  虽然可能还会惹你生气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你弟弟不仅仅是想要听歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想要看千早的笑容吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢唱歌  唱起来歌时总是喜笑颜开的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.44,0:16:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是最喜欢这样的姐姐的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  制作人也还有话要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「常规演唱会  有你出场的预定」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「歌迷  还有我们都等着你哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我也没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:16:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.67,0:17:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地方  动起来好像很容易碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解  马上就去确认
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  还没到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然千早她…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按惯例排成圆圈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.47,0:17:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,765事务…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对不起  我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早  终于来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:17:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我至少…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  伸出手来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,765事务…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  HIGH起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我  对你做了过分的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.52,0:18:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这种话不要说  不要说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到大家一起作的词  和优的画的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:19:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道能不能笑出来  唱出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.92,0:19:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想再试试
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早  差不多要到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  放松去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  是千早
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次居然会出场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  请暂时停止…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.59,0:20:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  请继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.27,0:20:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  果然已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.78,0:21:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.64,0:21:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.93,0:23:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周的偶像大师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.20,0:24:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次真是个好故事啊  太感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.11,0:24:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长  别回顾了  现在是要…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.18,0:24:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好  马上去椽子亭喝酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.73,0:24:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上班族伤不起啊
